{"tid":1467012,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[自亂陣腳]捉鬼篇","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:45.000Z","uid":290991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1e647968758f845a7b6baa348f755d35a055ae32","tid":1467012,"uid":290991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:30.000Z","msg":"無資格講捉鬼岩定錯<br />\n但現場最少一百幾十隻 你捉到幾時<br />\n比你捉到99隻出黎 咁又如何？<br />\n下次自然會補返99隻 有分別？<br />\n捉錯1隻你咪自傷1個貨真價實兄弟<br />\n捉到麻煩唔該盡快送隻瘟神走<br />\n唔好中出係隻鬼身<br />\n而家出黎係為捉鬼還是為光？<br />\n中出佢比你洩左度慾火咁又點？<br />\n攪清楚目標Pls"},{"pid":"cccc51adc128e5ec0b96f410c01a049e8b4fc56b","tid":1467012,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29393f4a4bedcb852cdea57cc3c96684e174fe4e","tid":1467012,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e647968758f845a7b6baa348f755d35a055ae32","tid":1467012,"uid":290991,"like":